    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1764764842\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>《坦佩利亚：恢弘之魂》作为一款竞技卡牌游戏</strong>，节奏紧张，策略性强，采用创新的明牌机制，包含大量生物、装备、能力和元素牌位，对战不会出现雷同。这款游戏的精彩，尽由玩家展现！<br>《坦佩利亚》明牌玩法别具匠心，两个牌组合二为一，<strong>生物牌和装备牌各20张，游戏机制与众不同</strong>。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>明牌玩法</strong> -《坦佩利亚：恢弘之魂》所有卡牌全部牌面朝上，明牌机制是这款游戏的一大创新，玩家可以直面对手，光明正大地对决！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/574a1d786bbab98b30173e05a5a56419.poster.avif?t=1764764842\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/574a1d786bbab98b30173e05a5a56419.webm?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/574a1d786bbab98b30173e05a5a56419.mp4?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>用实力说话</strong> - 凭借自身实力，跻身国际玩家前列。《坦佩利亚》与象棋相似，双方当前部署全部摆在台面。玩家需要充分利用明牌机制，运筹帷幄，赋予每一场对战不一样的精彩。击败你的对手，展现你的实力，一步一步向上攀登，占得《坦佩利亚：恢弘之魂》电子竞技世界的一席之地！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/b5a2c0b62d79ebce2639e903418cfc03.poster.avif?t=1764764842\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/b5a2c0b62d79ebce2639e903418cfc03.webm?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/b5a2c0b62d79ebce2639e903418cfc03.mp4?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>有限随机</strong> - 玩家必须头脑敏锐而且冷酷无情。《坦佩利亚》注重玩家自身的游戏能力，随机元素有限，偶然事件的影响极小。你是不是血冷如冰？你的游戏能力准备好接受考验没有？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/b98ceeb5efe7afc9d0ea7c799f4e02f6.poster.avif?t=1764764842\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/b98ceeb5efe7afc9d0ea7c799f4e02f6.webm?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/b98ceeb5efe7afc9d0ea7c799f4e02f6.mp4?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>源自玩家，心系玩家</strong> - 开发人员Enrico “Wolfillupo” Fedoni和Dario “Moonryde” Ferracci均为硬核玩家，也是游戏经验与专业经验丰富的Twitch主播，他们在游戏的设计阶段尤其考虑了玩家的需求。《坦佩利亚》这款游戏可谓源自玩家，心系玩家。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/d065ed35dd801fce19a4bb62d4050935.poster.avif?t=1764764842\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/d065ed35dd801fce19a4bb62d4050935.webm?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/d065ed35dd801fce19a4bb62d4050935.mp4?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>倾听玩家心声</strong> - 《坦佩利亚》经过了全球数百名玩家的测试，收获了如潮好评。开发团队采纳了测试玩家的反馈，进一步完善了游戏的相关方面。还等什么呢？快来体验《坦佩利亚：恢弘之魂》吧！欢迎分享你的想法和建议！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/51fbc5225f925fdca67336479903785f.poster.avif?t=1764764842\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/51fbc5225f925fdca67336479903785f.webm?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852780/extras/51fbc5225f925fdca67336479903785f.mp4?t=1764764842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
